thread.title: JUSTIN
thread.title_full: Redspot Car Rentals reviewed by JUSTIN

author: JUSTIN
title: JUSTIN
text: Our pre booked booster seat was not there then took 30 mins to be delivered and installed. There was a bag of food scraps in the boot and it was obvious the car had not even been vacuumed. there were lots of hidden fees and we ended up paying the same rate as budget or avis without the streamlined service. Just not worth it.
